item.title: gRPC Variant
item.description: gRPC Variant The gRPC variant allow injecting payloads in gRPC values (Active Scan Input Vector support). Active Scan Input Vectors Custom Values are injected into all key-value pairs in all gRPC values that are proxied through ZAP. See also gRPC for an overview of the gRPC add-on.
